    text: "The Camorra is a criminal organization from Italy. It started in the city of Naples around the 17th century. It is even older than the famous Sicilian Mafia. The Camorra began as a secret gang inside prisons to protect inmates. Later, it moved out into the city streets. The group is no single organization with one boss. Instead, it is made of many different clans or families. These families control specific neighborhoods and often fight each other for power. This makes them very violent and unpredictable. In the past, they acted like a shadow government. They helped poor people when the real government failed, but they also demanded money for protection. If a shop owner paid nothing, the Camorra would hurt them or destroy their business. Today, they are still very powerful. They are involved in illegal activities like drug trafficking and waste disposal. They have a strict code of silence. The Camorra remains a dangerous force in southern Italy, controlling many aspects of daily life through fear.",
